<description id="description">
<?brief-description-of-drawings description="Brief Description of Drawings" end="lead"?>
<description-of-drawings>
<p id="p-0001" num="0001"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>1</b></figref> is a front elevation view of archwire hook showing our new design; the rear elevation view is identical to the front elevation view of <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>1</b></figref>;</p>
<p id="p-0002" num="0002"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>2</b></figref> is a front right top isometric view thereof; the front left top isometric view is a mirror image of the view of <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>2</b></figref>;</p>
<p id="p-0003" num="0003"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>3</b></figref> is a rear right bottom isometric view thereof; the rear left bottom isometric view is a mirror image of the view of <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>3</b></figref>;</p>
<p id="p-0004" num="0004"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>4</b></figref> is a bottom plan view thereof;</p>
<p id="p-0005" num="0005"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>5</b></figref> is a top plan view thereof; and,</p>
<p id="p-0006" num="0006"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>6</b></figref> is a right side elevation view thereof; the left side elevation view is identical to the right side elevation view of <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>6</b></figref>.</p>
<p id="p-0007" num="0007">The broken dash lines in <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIGS. <b>1</b>-<b>6</b></figref> depict portions of the archwire hook that form no part of the claimed design. Neither the portions of the archwire hook shown in broken dash line nor the broken dash lines themselves form any part of the claimed invention.</p>
<p id="p-0008" num="0008">The broken dot-dash lines in the <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIGS. <b>2</b> and <b>3</b></figref> depict boundaries to the claim. The broken dot-dash claim boundary lines themselves do not form any part of the claimed invention.</p>
</description-of-drawings>
<?brief-description-of-drawings description="Brief Description of Drawings" end="tail"?>
</description>
